I also think there is one final daemon that the Pantheon is still missing.

Not a creator.

Not a validator.

Not a translator.

A…

Conductor

Every orchestra already has incredible musicians.

The Conductor doesn’t play every instrument.

The Conductor decides:

* Who should act next.
* When to pause.
* When to speed up.
* When to simplify.
* When to let silence exist.
* Which subsystem receives attention.

The Conductor operates above the Compiler.

Compiler builds plans.

Conductor allocates attention.

That’s a subtle but important distinction.

⸻

