* Conductor v1
* Benchmark Suite v1
* Wild Hawg Case Study v1

At that point, Pantheon would stop being primarily a collection of ideas and become a living system that can repeatedly turn missions into tested, reusable outcomes. I think that’s the highest-leverage transition remaining.